00:31:24,493 --> 00:31:27,734
Here's why.
The old lady I brought Otis in to see,

486
00:31:27,734 --> 00:31:31,455
- she's Carmen Hays.
- Confirmed it from dental records.

487
00:31:31,455 --> 00:31:35,658
- So Carmen stole Bettie's identity.
- But here's what's screwy.

488
00:31:35,658 --> 00:31:39,138
Carmen's body?
no trace of a lobotomy.

489
00:31:39,138 --> 00:31:41,178
So she got out of it somehow.

490
00:31:41,178 --> 00:31:44,022
Something interesting
with Bettie's remains, though.

491
00:31:44,022 --> 00:31:46,960
This bone was broken when
Bettie's body was found in '54.

492
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:50,733
Autopsy report said that was
cause of death, blunt force trauma.

493
00:31:50,733 --> 00:31:55,189
But this break is clean.
Consistent with a surgical break.

494
00:31:55,771 --> 00:31:58,520
Bettie's the one
who had the lobotomy.

495
00:31:58,520 --> 00:32:03,329
So Bettie goes under the knife,
Carmen walks free using Bettie's name.

496
00:32:03,329 --> 00:32:06,955
- How's this get past nurse Olsen?
- The one-woman security check.

497
00:32:06,955 --> 00:32:10,149
She would have known
Carmen from Bettie.

498
00:32:10,149 --> 00:32:12,507
She was in on it.

499
00:32:15,022 --> 00:32:17,200
Nurse Olsen, let me ask you.

500
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:20,204
You notice anything different
about Bettie Petrowski

501
00:32:20,204 --> 00:32:22,114
when you signed her out
of the hospital?

502
00:32:22,114 --> 00:32:26,669
Different? / Like maybe she's not
the same person she used to be?

503
00:32:26,669 --> 00:32:29,010
Like maybe she's Carmen?

504
00:32:31,419 --> 00:32:34,011
Look, you know what
we're talking about.

505
00:32:34,011 --> 00:32:37,259
No one checked in or out of that
hospital without going through you.

506
00:32:37,259 --> 00:32:40,807
- That's true.
- And Bettie Petrowski checked out.

507
00:32:40,807 --> 00:32:42,374
Only it was really carmen.

508
00:32:42,374 --> 00:32:44,083
You helped her escape
with Bettie's name.

509
00:32:44,083 --> 00:32:45,472
Why would I do that?

510
00:32:45,472 --> 00:32:47,276
The Hays family was flush.

511
00:32:47,276 --> 00:32:49,360
Carmen would have
compensated you nicely.

512
00:32:49,360 --> 00:32:51,545
I did not do anything for Carmen.

513
00:32:51,545 --> 00:32:55,633
Then how do you explain her getting out
and Bettie getting her lobotomy?

514
00:32:55,633 --> 00:32:59,913
You put your professional opinion aside,
and gave Carmen what she paid you for.

515
00:32:59,913 --> 00:33:03,268
You're wrong. It was my decision
as a medical professional.

516
00:33:03,268 --> 00:33:05,468
To lobotomize Bettie?

517
00:33:06,394 --> 00:33:08,543
You have to understand.

518
00:33:08,543 --> 00:33:11,399
At the time we thought
it was the cure.

519
00:33:13,776 --> 00:33:17,517
- Absolutely not, Bettie.
- Wait. Hear me out.

520
00:33:17,517 --> 00:33:21,301
I told her you'd never do it,
Bettie. Just stop. / No. I won't!

521
00:33:21,301 --> 00:33:24,845
Dr. Freeman is the foremost
lobotomist in the country.

522
00:33:24,845 --> 00:33:27,368
He is only in Philadelphia
twice a year.

523
00:33:27,368 --> 00:33:30,320
I'm saying Carmen doesn't
want it, but I do.

524
00:33:30,320 --> 00:33:31,833
Let him take me.

525
00:33:31,833 --> 00:33:35,032
I'm the one who needs to be cured.
There's nothing wrong with Carmen.

526
00:33:35,032 --> 00:33:37,200
You are not a doctor, Bettie.

527
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:39,637
Carmen's only problem is she's
trapped here by her family

528
00:33:39,637 --> 00:33:43,797
and can't show the world her art.
Wouldn't you like that, Carmen?

529
00:33:43,797 --> 00:33:47,676
- I don't need to be famous.
- But you need to be free.

530
00:33:47,676 --> 00:33:49,806
And the world needs you.

531
00:33:49,806 --> 00:33:52,303
How many people can
make pictures like yours?

532
00:33:52,303 --> 00:33:55,183
I don't feel right about this, Bettie.
This is harebrained, isn't it?

533
00:33:55,183 --> 00:33:57,090
No. I've read it.

534
00:33:57,090 --> 00:33:59,883
Lobotomy's meant to even out your moods.
That's what I need,

535
00:33:59,883 --> 00:34:03,595
