Please.

536
00:34:03,595 --> 00:34:07,511
Nurse, you said
Dr. Freeman's the best. / He is.

537
00:34:07,511 --> 00:34:09,319
This is my last chance.

538
00:34:09,319 --> 00:34:12,959
If I wait, Otis'll be moved on with
another mother, a lady from church.

539
00:34:12,959 --> 00:34:14,609
And I'll have to let him go.

540
00:34:14,609 --> 00:34:17,195
All I want to do is paint.

541
00:34:17,195 --> 00:34:19,757
All I want is Otis.

542
00:34:22,177 --> 00:34:24,831
I'm sure.

543
00:34:28,219 --> 00:34:30,211
Something in your plan
didn't go right,

544
00:34:30,211 --> 00:34:32,927
because Bettie never saw Otis again.

545
00:34:33,796 --> 00:34:38,229
- The snowstorm ruined our plan.
- How?

546
00:34:39,107 --> 00:34:41,774
Roads were closed.

547
00:34:41,774 --> 00:34:45,671
So instead of Bettie going to the private
hospital that Carmen had paid for,

548
00:34:45,671 --> 00:34:51,279
